[media] media: Add 1X16 16-bit raw bayer media bus code definitions

The codes will be called:

	MEDIA_BUS_FMT_SBGGR16_1X16
	MEDIA_BUS_FMT_SGBRG16_1X16
	MEDIA_BUS_FMT_SGRBG16_1X16
	MEDIA_BUS_FMT_SRGGB16_1X16

